{"tid":2233833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藏家稱毛澤東書法真跡遭竊 小偷竟嫌太長剪兩半","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T16:01:21.000Z","uid":337052,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"856659b1cffcd4f6ee6fe041838439fb863a5711","tid":2233833,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">藏家稱毛澤東書法真跡遭竊 小偷竟嫌太長剪兩半</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/10/07 19:40<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z4JmiYykHvnRUW2TDLsEQQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/962d0020-088b-11eb-b9d9-65db71e746ad\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz4JmiYykHvnRUW2TDLsEQQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F962d0020-088b-11eb-b9d9-65db71e746ad&h=2aadca74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者張謙香港7日電）<span class=\"red\">一幅聲稱是已故中共領袖毛澤東的書法真跡9月在香港被盜。港媒今天報導，警方循線逮捕了3名嫌犯，他們供述，由於這幅書法過長，不方便展示，盜取後已將作品一剪為二。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據官方香港電台報導，警方逮捕嫌犯後，找回這幅長2.8公尺的毛澤東書法真跡「紅軍第四軍司令部政治部布告」，但它已被剪成兩半。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，歹徒聲稱因為書法過長，難以展示，於是一剪為二。<br />\n<br />\n這幅聲稱是毛澤東書寫的真跡，為人稱「紅色收藏家」符春曉所有；9月10日，符春曉位於九龍油麻地的住所被盜，歹徒偷去了他的藏品。<br />\n<br />\n符春曉之後對外表示，被盜藏品有毛澤東的書法及大量舊郵票，價值港幣50億元（約合新台幣185億元），當中珍品包括上述長達2.8公尺的毛澤東書法真跡，以及目前在拍賣會上十分昂貴的中國大陸郵票「全國山河一片紅」。（編輯：繆宗翰）1091007<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202010070337.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202010070337.aspx&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=f3e9f3c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202010070337.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"267f620f699294f9bca3870db44f6ce1e858a38e","tid":2233833,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201007/390588599206285312.jpeg/Q5yATQtMzVIuiUoNV8IIYwL2Vl17J3m_rrzn266859s?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201007%2F390588599206285312.jpeg%2FQ5yATQtMzVIuiUoNV8IIYwL2Vl17J3m_rrzn266859s%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4b5ead52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17c173ac87b74b47c75d929222ff0689e23ce715","tid":2233833,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"收藏家符春曉上月油麻地寓所失竊，報稱價值約50億元的毛澤東親筆字畫、珍貴郵票及銅幣被盜，警方今拘3人並起回部分贓物，當中一幅報稱約值23億元、長2.8的書法被一分為二，原因竟是有人認為它「太長，難以展示」。今午符寓所無人應門，他仍身在內地休養，其秘書指，他已接獲警方通知，對書法被毀「他很傷心，他年紀大了，正在休息」。<br />\n<br />\n警方上月22日拘捕44歲姓林中國籍男子，涉嫌處理贓物，並在其灣仔住所起回部分主要贓物，包括2枚銅幣及一幅長2.8米報稱毛澤東親筆書法，不過書法已被一分為二，有人聲稱「覺得呢幅書法太長，難以展示，所以一剪為二」，目剪疑犯正保釋候查。"},{"pid":"c20ce192309c5af7eb11f98e6143ce9dcf62b3c5","tid":2233833,"uid":171786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾都有人偷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5e35993e38fde4897043f8dfb83728ce8ec5c7","tid":2233833,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c20ce192309c5af7eb11f98e6143ce9dcf62b3c5","tid":2233833,"uid":171786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾都有人偷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"習思想先係垃圾"},{"pid":"dd0b5c94561daddd60ef8afd08320d1478972116","tid":2233833,"uid":230693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"留名等睇習大大墨寶"},{"pid":"7a3a71ca6d646cb19cbe5641898ab72cf13faa6a","tid":2233833,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c20ce192309c5af7eb11f98e6143ce9dcf62b3c5","tid":2233833,"uid":171786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾都有人偷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surp